name: Finmos Tagge
content:
Finmos Tagge was a human male who served as Father of Chemicals in Coronet City on the planet Corellia during the High Republic Era. He was short and burly with a red beard. Around 230 BBY, Tagge, along with the other City Fathers, attended a gathering hosted by Alys Ongwa to honor recent losses in the city. He shared his last name with the House of Tagge, a human noble family connected to Tepasi.
Finmos Tagge appeared in the 2022 young-adult novel The High Republic: Midnight Horizon, written by Daniel Jos√© Older for the Star Wars: The High Republic multimedia project. Although his last name is Tagge, it is unknown if he has any connection to the House of Tagge.
